summary: Adds 3 pairs of ankle boots to the game. Meshes and textures are completely custom. They come in brown, black, and a pair with blank textures so you can have a go at texturing them yourself if you like. There is a 2k and 4k template in the textures folder. Requires NetImmerse Override. Use 'help ankle" in the console.
descriptionHtml:
Adds 3 pairs of ankle boots to the game. Meshes and textures are completely custom. They come in brown, black, and a pair with blank textures so you can have a go at texturing them yourself if you like. There is a 2k and 4k template in the textures folder. Requires NetImmerse Override. If you have RaceMenu you already have this, or you can get it directly here https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3748 . Use 'help ankle" in the console.

In the miscelaneous section there is a replacement .esp that adds High Heel sound to the boots. To use this file you will need to first visit Loverslab and download and install the High Heel Sound mod, or it will crash your game.Â  https://www.loverslab.com/files/file/1795-heels-sound/
